esight of real-time prices and uses an algorithm based on day-ahead forecasts, real-time market forecasts, and historical prices to decide charging/discharging thresholds.\n\nOverall, the page highlights the importance of bidding strategy and market conditions on battery storage revenues and suggests potential benefits from enhancing real-time market participation flexibility.",
